Package com.gridgraph.storage.heap.heapfile

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GraphHeapSpace
    A GraphHeapSpace represents heap file data organized into meaningful categories - thinking of it like a folder for a graph and sub-folders inside for all schemas of the graph into which block heap data (heap pages) and index data are put
    HeapFileUtils
    Utility operations on heap files
    HeapTypeConstants
    Internal values for heap file types
    Note that these constants values will be used as array index, so it's needed to keep them unique and values ranges starts from 0
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HeapType
    Type of heap file
